# Renderer (View)

## Rules

- **No direct database access** — use `window.api.*` from preload only
- Pages in `pages/`; reusable UI in `components/`
- UI orchestration in `viewmodels/` or hooks — not in presentational components
- Use shadcn components from `components/ui/` — do not duplicate primitives

## Stack patterns

- React Router for navigation
- React Hook Form + Zod for forms
- Tailwind + CSS variables from shadcn theme
- Toast for user-facing errors (technical detail goes to logs in main)

## Layout

- App shell: Sidebar + Header + content (`components/layout/`)
- Phase 0 pages: setup wizard, login shell, dashboard placeholder, settings

## Naming

- Components: PascalCase (`OrderForm.tsx`)
- Hooks/viewmodels: `use-*` prefix
